name: Found Someone You Have
Lore: '''I''m looking for someone.'' ''Looking? Found someone you have I would say.''',
Text: 'If you have a character of ability > 4 on table, use 3 Force to find one of your missing characters (your choice). OR During any control phase, examine the top card of your Lost Pile. If that card is a character of ability < 3, take that character into hand.',
